@startuml export_family
title Export: Diagrams, Tables, and Rendered Images

participant "Software Architect" as architect
participant "Export Commands" as bausteinsicht_cli_export_cmds
participant "Diagram" as bausteinsicht_diagram
participant "Table" as bausteinsicht_table
participant "Export" as bausteinsicht_export
participant "Document" as bausteinsicht_drawio_document

architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_export_cmds : 1. bausteinsicht export-diagram ‑‑view containers ‑‑diagram-format plantuml
bausteinsicht_cli_export_cmds -> bausteinsicht_diagram : 2. render(view, format: plantuml|mermaid|dot|d2)
bausteinsicht_diagram --> architect : 3. text diagram source (stdout or file)
architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_export_cmds : 4. bausteinsicht export-table ‑‑view containers ‑‑format adoc
bausteinsicht_cli_export_cmds -> bausteinsicht_table : 5. render(view, format: adoc|markdown)
bausteinsicht_table --> architect : 6. table source (stdout or file)
architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_export_cmds : 7. bausteinsicht export ‑‑view containers
bausteinsicht_cli_export_cmds -> bausteinsicht_export : 8. read synced draw.io page, invoke headless draw.io CLI
bausteinsicht_export -> bausteinsicht_drawio_document : 9. read diagram page
bausteinsicht_export --> architect : 10. PNG / SVG file

@enduml
